cs.AR, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.ET, cs.DC

This paper involves the exploration of neural architectures and heterogeneous ASIC accelerator designs, which falls under the category of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Computer Systems and Control (cs.SY). Additionally, it involves the optimization of latency, energy, and area, which falls under the category of Electronic and Computer Engineering (cs.ET) and Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC). Finally, the paper proposes a framework for co-exploration, which falls under the category of Architecture (cs.AR).
